	<div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="//dealbook.nytimes.com/2014/12/03/morning-agenda-big-law-bolsters-bonuses/" data-title="Morning Agenda: Big Law Bolsters Bonuses" data-description="Big law firms are bringing back hefty bonuses for associates. | A scramble to fix Europe&#039;s banks. | Bank of New York Mellon gives a board seat to the Trian Fund. | How the bond king lost his empire.">
